summary: Fractured. A Yoonmin/Taehopekook/Namjin Infamous AU. Chapter 15/? The world was falling apart, and somehow Park Jimin had become...
caption:
Fractured. A Yoonmin/Taehopekook/Namjin Infamous AU.

Chapter 15/?

The world was falling apart, and somehow Park Jimin had become an unwilling member of its unravelling. After developing powers beyond his wildest dreams, Jimin is thrust head first into danger, into a war he never asked to partake in.

In war you’ve got to take sides, even if that means joining up with an infamous group of rebels who turn out to be a lot less intimidating than Jimin originally thought. Well, all except for a certain dark haired male who seems to be set on making Jimin as uncomfortable as possible, and whose persona has graced the news one too many times for Jimin’s liking.

All Jimin wanted to do was graffiti some damn walls.
